//
//           # Contribution of this triangle to each of its three vertex weights.
//           # Uses Gauss-Legendre quadrature (here: 7-point rule on triangle).
//           # For closed-form Appendix A, replace quadrature with the analytic
//           # arctangent/logarithm formula from Lipman 2008.
